Package: avstrat
Title: Tools for Generating Stratigraphic Sections
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matt", "Loewen", 
    email = "mloewen@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5621-285X"))
Description: Tools for data processing and generating stratigraphic sections 
    for volcanic deposits and tephrastratigraphy. Package was developed for
    studies on Alaska volcanoes ("av") where stratigraphic ("strat") figures 
    are needed for interpreting eruptive histories, but the methods are applicable
    to any sediment stratigraphy project. 
